<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=16046&amp;p=197613#p197613"><![CDATA[
That left scrolling crawl is something related to the 2C02's normally missing pixel. The HDNES is <em>supposed</em> to intentionally omit four master clock cycles to the PPU whenever it notices the missing pixel, but for whatever reason it's not working for you.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3512">lidnariq</a> — Tue Jun 06, 2017 12:18 pm</p><hr />
